{"atom_id":"ig34_p0137_a025","source":"SDTMIG_v3.4","page":137,"page_region":"middle","parent_section":"§6.2 AE – Adverse Events","atom_type":"LIST_ITEM","verbatim":"a. AETERM captures the verbatim term collected for the event. It is the topic variable for the AE dataset. AETERM is a required variable and must have a value.","heading_level":null,"sibling_index":null,"figure_ref":null,"cross_refs":[],"extracted_by":{"subagent_type":"oh-my-claudecode:executor","prompt_version":"P0_writer_pdf_v1.1+","ts":"2026-04-24T00:00:00Z"}}
