{"atom_id":"ig34_p0137_a029","source":"SDTMIG_v3.4","page":137,"page_region":"middle","parent_section":"§6.2 AE – Adverse Events","atom_type":"LIST_ITEM","verbatim":"c. AEDECOD is the preferred term derived by the sponsor from the coding dictionary. It is a required variable and must have a value. It is expected that the reported term (AETERM) will be coded using a standard dictionary such as MedDRA. The sponsor is expected to provide the dictionary name and version used to map the terms utilizing the external codelist element in the Define-XML document.","heading_level":null,"sibling_index":null,"figure_ref":null,"cross_refs":[],"extracted_by":{"subagent_type":"oh-my-claudecode:executor","prompt_version":"P0_writer_pdf_v1.1+","ts":"2026-04-24T00:00:00Z"}}
